snippet.title: FIFA 23 | Official FIFA World Cup Deep Dive Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the FIFA World Cup™ for free in FIFA 23 from November 9: https://www.ea.com/games/fifa/fifa-23/world-cup

00:00 - Intro
00:37 - Game Modes
02:05 - Matchday Experience

Experience football’s biggest tournament in FIFA 23 with all 32 teams, an authentic matchday experience, and the chance to play your way with online, offline, live, and custom tournament modes. Plus enjoy a full Season of content in FIFA Ultimate Team to give you the ultimate connection to the FIFA World Cup.

Get FIFA 23 now and play the FIFA World Cup from November 9: https://www.ea.com/games/fifa/fifa-23/buy
